Cell["\<\
f is reducible by g if some monomial m in f is a multiple of a leading \
monomial g_i in G.  If m is the leading monomial in f then f is \
lead-reducible by g.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8272320874614167`*^9, 3.827232148978077*^9}},
